
- An iframe embedding a YouTube video
- An image with alt text
- A <details>/<summary> accordion element
- A <figure> with <figcaption>
Test that the iframe loads and the accordion expands/collapses.






<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Simple Page of Links by Poornima</title>
</head>

<body>

<h2>YouTube Video</h2>

<!-- Iframe -->
<iframe width="300" height="200"
src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/tgbNymZ7vqY">
</iframe>

<br><br>

<!-- Image with alt -->
<h2>Image</h2>
<img src="https://tse1.mm.bing.net/th/id/OIP.I-qC7OzdAMhriVu9gOOySwHaEK?rs=1&pid=ImgDetMain&o=7&rm=3" alt="Sample Image">

<br><br>

<!-- Details / Summary -->
<h2>More Info</h2>
<details>
    <summary>Click to expand</summary>
    <p>This is hidden content. It appears when you click.</p>
</details>
  
  <br><br>

<!-- Figure with caption -->
<h2>Figure Example</h2>
<figure>
    <img src="https://tse1.mm.bing.net/th/id/OIP.I-qC7OzdAMhriVu9gOOySwHaEK?rs=1&pid=ImgDetMain&o=7&rm=3" alt="Example Image">
    <figcaption>This is an image with a caption</figcaption>
</figure>

</body>
</html>
  
